lead_paragraph: Blake Griffin scored 25 points and the Los Angeles Clippers beat the Oklahoma City Thunder 110-108 on Friday night to improve their best start in franchise history to 8-1.

headline.print_headline: Griffin Scores 25 to Help Clippers Beat Thunder 110-108
